1- MAGIC LINK

POST /lien-magique
params: 'email'

Model MagicLink
  user_id
  expired_at (1.day)
  signature (MD5 user_id-expired_at-user_email)

-> email sent
  contains link to /lien-magique avec la signature comme query string

GET /lien-magique
params: signature
-> returns JWT in headers (change dispatch_requests)

